# Kompl contributing (repo rules)

## Commits

- **DCO required**: every commit must use `git commit -s` (`Signed-off-by` trailer). PRs fail DCO check without it. Fix: `git rebase HEAD~N --signoff && git push --force-with-lease`.
- **Conventional Commits**: `feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`, `test:` — optional scope; body explains *why*.
- **Author**: tuirk only. No `Co-authored-by:`. No AI/Claude in commit messages or code comments.
- **No commit/push** unless the user explicitly asks.

## `main` branch protection (ruleset `main-protection`)

- 1 approving review required; stale reviews dismissed on push.
- **Required status checks** (strict, branch must be up to date): `unit-tests-app`, `unit-tests-cli`, `unit-tests-nlp`, `integration-test`.
- Also runs on PRs: DCO, CodeQL, Scorecard, Dependabot (DCO not in ruleset but enforced in practice).
- Admin bypass enabled (solo maintainer).

## After push

```bash
gh run list --limit 1
gh run watch <id> --exit-status
```

After merge milestone: `npx gitnexus@1.6.1 analyze` (add `--embeddings` if `.gitnexus/meta.json` stats.embeddings > 0).

## PR template

- Sign off every commit; explain why; note how tested.
- Prefer PRs under ~300 lines; large deps need issue first.

## Blocked pip upgrades (do not merge Dependabot until resolved)

- **chromadb** pinned `0.4.24` — `numpy<2` required (`np.float_` removed in NumPy 2). PRs bumping chromadb to 1.x or numpy to 2.x must be **closed** until a deliberate chromadb migration (integration test + vector_store API).
- **mcp-server `qs`**: use `package.json` override `>=6.15.2 <7.0.0` (GHSA-q8mj-m7cp-5q26); lockfile-only bump via Dependabot is insufficient without override.

## Dependabot

- Weekly Mon 09:00 UTC: `app/`, `cli/`, `mcp-server/`, `nlp-service/`, github-actions, docker.
- `@types/node` ignored for `>=25` in npm ecosystems.

## Security deferrals

- Scorecard pip hash-pinning #40/#41/#62: intentional — see `docs/security/scorecard-deferred.md`.
